# Asset Register (Flask)
- App code lives under `asset-register/`; SQLite via `database.py` (`sqlite3` / file path from `DATABASE_PATH`).
- Production DB path on EC2: `/opt/asset-register/data/asset_register.sqlite` (matches Terraform backup cron).
- ISO / audit expectations (when you add an `assets` model): validate unique asset tags; log update/delete to an `audit_trail` with previous/new value, action, and timestamp.
